303551.title: Inspector Gadget's Last Case
303551.description: Gadget says goodbye to his beloved Gadgetmobile and buys a new car to replace it. Meanwhile, evil Dr. Claw hatches a plan to cost Gadget his badge.

398630.title: Tad: The Lost Explorer
398630.description: Tad is a bored construction worker dreaming of a life of adventure until one day he is mistaken for a famous archeologist and that dream comes true.

454623.title: The Teacher From the Black Lagoon
454623.description: A boy imagines the worst about his teacher, Mrs. Green, on the first day of school.  This wildly funny look into the mind of every child will become an instant classic.

465526.title: Funny Pets 2
465526.description: A dog, a sassy cat, and an outspoken parrot watch funny pets on TV when their owners leave out, arguing over which pet should win the funniest title.

466030.title: Chop Kick Panda
466030.description: A pudgy, idle panda only fantasizes of becoming a Taekwondo master, but when an evil tiger threatens his village, he must put his dream into action.

466956.title: Thunder and the House of Magic
466956.description: A lost cat finds shelter in the enchanted home of a retired magician but the man’s scheming nephew also has some tricks up his sleeve.

473892.title: Ivan the Incredible
473892.description: A young boy, targeted by bullies, sees changes when a witch brews up a magic potion that makes him "the best at everything" for one day.

490049.title: Tom & Jerry and Friends
490049.description: The Van Beuren Tom and Jerry. Not the famous cat and mouse, but a human duo that lasted for just under 30 cartoons between 1931 and 1933.

499245.title: Bad Baby
499245.description: There’s no stopping this naughty little toddler, despite the best efforts from his well-meaning father, exhausted mother, and frustrated sister.

499640.title: Father's Day
499640.description: Take a deep dive into this animated adventure where sea creatures big and small compete for the top prize in the annual Deep Sea Burp Contest.

521851.title: A.C.O.R.N.S.: Operation Crackdown
521851.description: With the lives of his friends hanging in the balance, a crafty squirrel concocts a plan to retrieve a stolen nut supply from a corrupt corporation.

521981.title: April Fools Fright
521981.description: It’s Halloween in Grimmsburgh, or is it? Selma the Witch’s April Fool’s Day spell on the townsfolk has them believing it’s time to trick or treat!

528867.title: Return to Treasure Island
528867.description: After Jim Hawkins discovers Captain Bones' treasure map, he’s off on an exciting and dangerous adventure, where anything is possible.

530643.title: A Wizard's Tale
530643.description: A reluctant hero travels to a magical kingdom where he must find a crystal key to ward off a mean-spirited wizard and find happiness.

532505.title: The Lion Kid 2
532505.description: After a brief vacation, Tuckerville's brave sheriff Kidd Mane is kicked out of his post by the Mayor, Mr. Tucker. Now, Kid Mane must win back his job.

537356.title: Snowtime!
537356.description: When winter break comes to a small village, an 11-year-old boy and girl lead opposing teams of kids and engage in a long and epic snowball fight.

541243.title: Little Bite in the Big City
541243.description: A plucky cockroach living inside a computer struggles to survive an ongoing street battle between pigeons and beetles and win his dream girl.

568579.title: Turkey Day
568579.description: After a Thanksgiving turkey is hypnotized, he officially cancels the holiday and travels back to the Jurassic era. Who will save him?

571130.title: Dummies
571130.description: In this silent short, a bored dummy watches the days pass from his small shop, until the opening of a new store next to his changes his life forever.

571561.title: Snow White and the Magic Mirror
571561.description: Snow White takes refuge with seven hilarious dwarves while trying to outwit an evil queen in this comedic take on the classic fairy tale.

574345.title: The GadgetGang in Outer Space
574345.description: After crash landing on Earth, a group of funny aliens discovers the wonders of the new planet, until they realize the whole galaxy is in peril.

579028.title: Alien Busters
579028.description: After a wicked intergalactic lizard zaps all creatures of their senses of humor, it’s up to an elite group of heroes to save comedy!

579029.title: Pets 2
579029.description: The hilarious trio of animal pals snuggles up on the couch to watch cats being cats in the best way possible: silly, funny, and fierce!

579030.title: St. Paddy
579030.description: A darling leprechaun sets out with a simple goal: to make the world luckier by bringing happiness to people in the form of wishes come true!

584969.title: Outlandish
584969.description: The silly things we humans do take center stage in this song-based comedy series that tries to make sense of what often appears to be total nonsense.

595349.title: Aliens Next Door
595349.description: Transferred to a new job, the Peoples family arrive on the planet Bolognia. Feeling very insecure about the move, they become even more intimidated by the sight of their hosts who are green, spotted and have antennae! Almost as frightened are their new Bolognian neighbors Charlick and Mavo Zox. When little Benny Peoples gets "lost", he unwittingly brings the two families together.

603551.title: Boonie Bears: The Big Top Secret
603551.description: When Briar is washed away in a flood and ends up in the company of a traveling circus, his brother must embark on a grand journey to bring him home.

605770.title: Maya the Bee 2: The Honey Games
605770.description: Following an unproductive harvest season, it’s up to Maya and her brave friends to save their hive by competing in a series of games.

608883.title: Animalympics
608883.description: The cartoon classic with comedy icons Gilda Radner, Billy Crystal, and Harry Shearer as the voice of animals competing in their own Olympics games!

629546.title: Even Mice Belong in Heaven
629546.description: After a mouse passes away, she is sent to heaven where she meets a fox and the two become an unlikely pair of pals. Together, they take on adventures.

649752.title: Sheep & Wolves
649752.description: After a wolf is transformed into a sheep, he must work hard to gain the friendship of his fellow sheep to protect him from vicious wolf attacks.

0300007182.title: Erky Perky
0300007182.description: Two bugs, Erky, and his friend, the cowardly and impressionable Perky, live an idyllic life on a downtown hot dog stand until one day they are swept away in a take-out bag and end up in a sterile suburban kitchen with no food in sight. The two bickering, dimwitted and lazy bugs are forced to survive in the new and scary "Land of Kitchen". Every day, they are obsessed with finding food, and eventually finding their way home to the "Hot Dog Stand". Their quests are almost always befouled by 'Mad' Margaret, the self-appointed ruler of Kitchen, and her 'sidekick' Cecil.

03855.title: Numb Chucks
03855.description: Two dim-witted woodchuck vigilantes try to be awesome and save the citizens of their land by using kung fu skills that they don't even have.

0300007689.title: Bubble Bip
0300007689.description: The hilarious adventures of Bubble Bip, a video game hero who slings bubbles at sassy squids, and the zany group of Earth kids he makes friends with.

04834.title: Talking Tom and Friends
04834.description: Meet Angela, Ben, Hank, and Ginger, a team of tech-savvy friends who are always ready to laugh and have some exciting adventures together.

02101.title: Almost Naked Animals
02101.description: Even though the title may suggest otherwise, "Almost Naked Animals" is an animated series geared toward kids. The show's main setting is the Banana Cabana, a seemingly ordinary, run-of-the-mill beachfront hotel. What's not ordinary about the hotel is who (or what) runs it -- animals who are all shaved and wearing underwear. The Banana Cabana's top dog is Howie, who would barely be able to keep things under control without his crew helping him out. That crew includes jittery desk clerk Octo, sugary-sweet activities director Bunny and duck-of-all-trades Duck.

0300004882.title: IMP
0300004882.description: A light-hearted look at trying to square a career spreading the evil with the mundane demands of the domestic life.

0300006130.title: Oggy Y Las Cucarachas
0300006130.description: Es bueno como el pan, no mataría una mosca y sería el más feliz de los gatos si tres horrendas cucarachas no se hubieran mudado a su cómodo hogar.

04835.title: Talking Tom and Friends Minis
04835.description: The funny friends bring a sense of adventure to their everyday world, where even the most ordinary things have the potential to be extraordinary.

0300005179.title: 3 Amigonauts
0300005179.description: Three friends in the far-off future go to the best space academy in the solar system and find themselves in far-out adventures all the time!

0300008383.title: Flea-Bitten!
0300008383.description: After escaping the pound, a dog and his wisecracking flea buddy set off on an off-leash adventure in the city while searching for his family.

0300004700.title: Camp Lakebottom
0300004700.description: A little boy gets on the wrong bus for summer camp, befriending two other kids before they end up at a weird, adventurous camp with a new enemy.

02089.title: Best Ed
02089.description:
Best Ed is about the unlikely friendship between a dog named Ed and a squirrel named Buddy. Ed wakes up every morning to be the best Ed he can be, even though it drives Buddy bonkers. But for every funny blunder Buddy suffers, thanks to Ed’s cloying good deeds, Buddy knows that…although it’s hard to live with Ed…it’s harder to live without him. They’re not just friends, they’re best friends.
Meet the new odd couple for kids…one best Buddy. And one Best Ed!

0300006437.title: Toca Life Stories
0300006437.description: Four pals take on a variety of fun-filled adventures, like petting the tiniest of animals, overcoming stagefright, and trying all kinds of new stuff.

0300007816.title: Ned's Newt
0300007816.description: Ned, a little boy with a big imagination, gave his pet newt too much to eat and it became a 500-pound best friend, Newton, who is extra fun!

0300007168.title: Sidekick
0300007168.description: Most kids dream of being superheroes. Not Eric Needles. Eric dreams of being a sidekick. So you can imagine his elation when his favorite superhero, Maxum Man, selects Eric to be his sidekick. But things take a weird turn when, on the day that Eric is scheduled to start being a full-time sidekick, Maxum Man vanishes.

01606.title: League of Super Evil
01606.description: Armed with a whole new approach to badness, The League of Super Evil (a.k.a. L.O.S.E.) follows four Super Villains who have set their sights on nothing less than total neighbourhood domination! L.O.S.E. is helmed by the diminutive Great Voltar, whose grandiose plans are generally miniscule and child-like and give new meaning to the term lowered expectations. Then theres gadgeteer Doktor Frogg, whose evil genius is diminished only by his incredible bad luck. Bringing the muscle is former Siberian farm-boy Reginald Red Menace, who prefers to channel his energy into gardening, cute animals and bouncy castles. And we cant forget the completely unpredictable Doomageddon, a pan-dimensional hell-hound who brings the term bad dog to a whole other level.

02182.title: Simon's Cat
02182.description: Simon's Cat is an animated series featuring the mischievous and often hilarious antics of a fat white cat and his owner, Simon.  Launched in 2008, Simon’s Cat has since become one of the most popular animated channels on YouTube, with millions of fans around the world!
